of what Ignacio wrote?

819
00:59:11,800 --> 00:59:12,600
No.

820
00:59:14,100 --> 00:59:14,700
What a pity!

821
00:59:15,800 --> 00:59:18,000
Are you from a publisher too?

822
00:59:18,500 --> 00:59:21,100
No. What publisher?

823
