896
01:03:42,800 --> 01:03:44,300
So you'll let me audition?

897
01:03:55,100 --> 01:03:57,400
<i>The audition worked
for several months,</i>

898
01:03:58,000 --> 01:04:01,500
<i>long enough for me to throw myself
into the shooting of "The Visit",</i>

899
01:04:01,700 --> 01:04:04,200
<i>like the woman who
threw herself to the crocodiles</i>

900
01:04:04,400 --> 01:04:07,000
