is really heavy, man.

909
01:04:44,200 --> 01:04:47,000
For you, as an actor,
it's much more intresting.

910
01:04:47,200 --> 01:04:48,000
You think so?

911
01:04:48,200 --> 01:04:48,700
Of course.

912
01:04:50,400 --> 01:04:52,900
<i>I shot "The Visit"
as a homage to Ignacio.</i>

913
01:04:53,200 --> 01:04:56,300
<i>In his letter, he'd said
he'd love to see it on the screen.</i>

914
01:04:56,600 --> 01:04:58,700
<i>And also to discover
the enigma of Juan.</i>

915
01:04:59,800 --> 01:05:02,300
<i>He allowed me
