916
01:05:02,500 --> 01:05:04,000
<i>but only physically.</i>

917
01:05:05,000 --> 01:05:08,700
<i>We were about to finish shooting
and his mystery was still intact.</i>

918
01:05:09,400 --> 01:05:10,600
<i>But on the last day</i>

919
01:05:11,100 --> 01:05:12,600
<i>we had a visit.</i>

920
