922
01:05:17,800 --> 01:05:18,500
Rolling!

923
01:05:19,200 --> 01:05:21,500
"The Visit"
91, 1, first take.

924
01:05:22,500 --> 01:05:23,700
Zahara, darling!

925
01:05:24,100 --> 01:05:25,100
Action!

926
