Do you want to kidnap me?

929
01:05:36,900 --> 01:05:38,100
Open the door!

930
01:05:38,500 --> 01:05:41,500
I have to take a piss,
buy cigarettes, get a fix!

931
01:05:41,700 --> 01:05:43,300
