933
01:05:47,100 --> 01:05:48,200
You'll never be sure.

934
01:05:48,500 --> 01:05:50,300
That's my revenge.

935
01:05:58,400 --> 01:05:59,700
Let me out or I'll scream.

936
01:06:00,500 --> 01:06:01,700
I loved Ignacio.

937
01:06:03,000 --> 01:06:06,600
You don't love a boy of ten.
