966
01:08:09,800 --> 01:08:11,700
And there are no witnesses.

967
01:08:13,200 --> 01:08:14,300
God.

968
01:08:14,600 --> 01:08:15,500
Yes,

969
01:08:15,900 --> 01:08:17,200
but He's on our side.

970
